[[TITLE]] Skillshare Grant Contract
[[TITLE]] <%= @project %>
[[TITLE]] Dated: <%= @date %>

[[HEADING]] Overview
This student agreement is between the student and Firefly Arts Collective regarding the submitted proposal for attending <%= @project %>.

The student, <%= @artist %>, desires to receive grant funding to attend <%= @project %> for the purpose of furthering their artistic skill.  Firefly Arts Collective has agreed to provide funding in the amount of <%= @amount %> USD for the class as determined by the Art Grant Core.  The student shall not make any changes to the proposed class to be attended without obtaining approval from a representative of Firefly Arts Collective's Art Core.

All parties agree to the terms presented below.  Violation of any of the following terms may result in:

  1. Forfeiture of the grant provided,
  2. Repayment of all grant funds received by the student for the class.

[[HEADING]] Funding

  1. Firefly Arts Collective will disburse 100% of the grant funding upon receiving the signed contract.

  2. The student agrees that this grant of <%= @amount %> USD shall represent the total sum they will receive from Firefly Arts Collective and the student hereby agrees to assume responsibility for any additional costs beyond the the grant amount incurred in the attendance of <%= @project %>.

[[HEADING]] Events

  3. The student agrees to meet the following schedule of events, under the given schedule:
    [[SUBHEADING]] 1. Class Attendance (<%= @values["skill_attend_day"] %>)]
    The funded class will be completed by <%= @values["skill_attend_day"] %>.

  4. The student agrees to furnish Firefly Arts Collective with documentation of attendance the class, including one or more of the following: receipt, report card, or signed note from an instructor on official educational facility letterhead.

[[HEADING]] Liability

  5. The student agrees not to hold Firefly Arts Collective responsible for injury and/or damage caused by the negligent acts of the student or third parties.  The student further agrees that Firefly Arts Collective, its agents, and its associates may not be held responsible for any damage to, nor destruction of, any persons or property in the course of attending the class, and the artist hereby waives any such claims.
[[PAGEBREAK]]
The artist hereby acknowledges that they have reviewed, understand, and agree to the terms set forth in this agreement.

[[SIGNATURES]]
